@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy & Data Protection";
}

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 border-bottom pb-3 mb-4">
                <i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill text-danger display-5"></i>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-0">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
                    <small class="text-muted">Last Updated: @DateTime.UtcNow.ToString("MMMM dd, yyyy")</small>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p class="lead text-secondary mb-5">
                At ePizzaHub, we value your trust and are committed to safeguarding your personal transaction properties. This document clarifies how our framework manages, secures, and maps data elements.
            </p>

            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 p-4 mb-4 bg-light">
                <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3"><i class="bi bi-cookie text-danger me-2"></i>1. Tracking Cookies & Active Session Keys</h4>
                <p class="text-secondary mb-0">
                    To maintain transactional continuity, our engine establishes an encrypted memory tracker parameter (<code class="text-danger">CustomerSessionUid</code>) when you browse our storefront menu layouts. This cookie tracks anonymous item quantities and shopping basket models across state transitions, preventing your choices from resetting to zero.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 p-4 mb-4 bg-light">
                <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3"><i class="bi bi-database-fill-check text-danger me-2"></i>2. Core Order Information Processing</h4>
                <p class="text-secondary mb-3">
                    When pushing data variables downstream via our Checkout channel operations, we collect the necessary context parameters to fulfill food deliveries safely:
                </p>
                <ul class="text-secondary ps-4 mb-0">
                    <li class="mb-2"><strong>Identity Profiles:</strong> Customer profile mapping tags, email handles, and verified authorization hashes.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><strong>Location Properties:</strong> Street address variables and delivery routing targets.</li>
                    <li class="mb-0"><strong>Transaction Logs:</strong> Aggregated subtotal amounts and payment method type tokens.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 p-4 mb-4 bg-light">
                <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-3"><i class="bi bi-eye-slash-fill text-danger me-2"></i>3. External Data Sharing Restrictions</h4>
                <p class="text-secondary mb-0">
                    We enforce strict network endpoint segregation. Third-party actors cannot query your internal transactional payload databases. Session identifiers are kept private and expire automatically after 30 minutes of inactivity.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center mt-5">
                <a asp-controller="Pizzas" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-outline-danger rounded-pill px-4 py-2 fw-bold shadow-sm">
                    <i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-2"></i>Return to Menu Marketplace
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>